RSMVC (beta)

Requirements:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
 ~ PHP >= 5.1.0 (PDO and object model)
 ~ Apache's mod_rewrite


Setup:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
 ~ Make any subfolders of /system/tmp/ writable (chmod 777)
 ~ Edit the config: /config/config.php


Code/filename convention:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Models
 ~ /application/models/ExampleNameModel.php
 ~ class ExampleNameModel extends Model
 ~ For database reference, use $this->pdo

Controllers
 ~ /application/controllers/ExampleNameController.php
 ~ class ExampleNameController extends Controller

Views
 ~ /application/views/example_name.php

URLs
 ~ URL's may only contain lowercase alphanumeric characters, dashes and forward slashes